<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạlsẖwqy wḥnyny ạn ạ̉ltqy̱ bạllh tmtly ʿynạy mn mrạh
 syḍmny fy ạlạ̉ḥḍạn ʿnd dẖạ stmsḥ ạlạ̉ḥzạn
 sậrạh sậrạh wsyạ̉ty dẖạ ạlywm ạldẖy fyh ạ̉rạh
 2- yạ ạ̹lhy ʿd qlby llqạ ạlqryb ʿnd mrậk nfsy tṭyb
 ttsyny ạlạḥzạn wtgẖmrny bạlḥnạn
 sậrạk sậrạk wsyạ̉ty dẖạ ạlywm ạldẖy fyh ậrạk</lyrics>
